# Blade templates (legacy)

- The main storefront frontend is **not Blade** anymore; it lives in a separate Vue project.
- In this repo, Blade is mostly **legacy remnants** to be removed over time.
- **Do not add new Blade pages/views** for new storefront/public UI features.

## Allowed / expected Blade usage

- **Transactional emails** under `src/resources/views/emails/**` are expected to remain Blade.
- **XML views/feeds** under `src/resources/views/xml/**` are supported and may be extended when needed.
- **Filament views** under `src/resources/views/filament/**` are supported and may be extended when needed.
- Some Blade usage may still exist for legacy admin or internal tools; prefer migrating those flows to Filament when feasible.
